to use you will need PyOpenCL and PyOpenGL




to install PyOpenCL you must get it from the git repo in order to have GL interop
git clone http://git.tiker.net/trees/pyopencl.git
TO BUILD (on MAC):
    cd pyopencl
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    python configure.py --cl-enable-gl
    make
    sudo make install

http://mathema.tician.de/software/pyopencl


you can install PyOpenGL any normal python way (easy_install or from the website)
